						<div class="postbody">Even when controlling every line, 
<br />
<br />P address bus = 19 (for 512k) 
<br />P data bus = 8
<br />c address bus = 19 (for 512k)
<br />
<br />control bus = 20 at most (with memory card interface)
<br />
<br />That's 66 I/O... 74 if you use the PLD to write CHR memory.</div>

